{"tid":469504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[駙馬爺點算]津巴布韋發生軍事政變","createTime":"2017-11-15T11:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T10:47:41.000Z","uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"380260b0f817daf5c00677b3fb66b25dc3d6817d","tid":469504,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=243270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D243270&d=ldFL%2FGoPYvM%2FPjc8ZZXggF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9f4edc48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D243270&h=6a931103\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=243270</a><br />\n<br />\n兩岸國際<br />\n<br />\n津巴布韋懷疑軍事政變<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】津巴布韋懷疑發生軍事政變。<br />\n<br />\n在首都哈拉雷街頭氣氛緊張，多處都有坦克及軍人駐守，市中心曾傳出多響爆炸聲，並有軍人接管國營電視台。<br />\n<br />\n在總統穆加貝的家門外也有大批士兵包圍，暫時未知穆加貝的情況。目擊者表示，看到大批軍車正駛往首都。<br />\n<br />\n93歲、執政逾30年的穆加貝，上周突然革除獲軍方支持的副總統，政局隨即陷入混亂。<br />\n<br />\n軍方司令奇旺加在星期一表示，軍方會介入令國家政局回復平靜，穆加貝的政黨指摘軍方叛變。<br />\n<br />\n由於局勢緊張，美國駐津巴布韋大使館宣布暫時關閉，指示所有職員留在家中，並呼籲在津巴布韋的美國人注意安全。"},{"pid":"d4b5442841075c9d39735504924c38425fa88ce2","tid":469504,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"果位公主會點？"},{"pid":"572bc3ccfc75f9091e8095fe77deba7c617ecea6","tid":469504,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家唔想理"},{"pid":"65a8c252be000c79c41a901469cae0c60a8af0de","tid":469504,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:47:41.000Z","msg":"高登巴打點呀？ 有冇報平安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}